OL,3,CWorld Cup 2026: Fifa unveils new ball
OL,4,Cwhich uses AI to help referees
OL,6,FThe official match ball of the 2026
OL,7,FWorld Cup will use state-of-the-art
OL,8,Ftechnology to provide more insight
OL,9,Finto gameplay and help referees make
OL,10,Ffaster decisions.
OL,12,FFifa unveiled the new ball - named the
OL,13,FTrionda - on Friday.
OL,15,FNext year's tournament is being co-
OL,16,Fhosted by the United States, Canada
OL,17,Fand Mexico. The name Trionda is a
OL,18,Fcombination of "tri", the English
OL,19,Fprefix for three - representing the
OL,20,Fthree host nations, and "onda", the
OL,21,FSpanish word for "wave".
