OL,3,CWorld Cup 2026: Fifa unveils new ball
OL,4,Cwhich uses AI to help referees
OL,6,FDesigned by Adidas, each ball is
OL,7,Ffitted with an AI chip that will send
OL,8,Flive data to the video assistant
OL,9,Freferee system (VAR) to assist with
OL,10,Foffside and handball calls.
OL,12,FAdidas claims its innovative
OL,13,F'connected ball technology' will
OL,14,Fenable faster in-game officiating
OL,15,Fdecisions.
OL,17,FIt says the real-time data sent to
OL,18,FVAR, combined with player position
OL,19,Fdata, should provide faster rulings.
