OL,3,CWorld Cup 2026: Fifa unveils new ball
OL,4,Cwhich uses AI to help referees
OL,6,FThe technology can also help identify
OL,7,Feach individual touch of the ball and
OL,8,Fhas been created with the host
OL,9,Fnations' differing climates and
OL,10,Fweather conditions in mind.
OL,12,FAdidas says the icons embossed on the
OL,13,Fthe ball's surface will increase grip
OL,14,F` especially in damp conditions.
OL,16,FThe 2026 World Cup will kick off at
OL,17,FMexico City's Estadio Azteca on June
OL,18,F11 and culminate at East Rutherford,
OL,19,FNew Jersey, on July 19.
